do n't kill it is a 2016 horror comedy film directed and edited by mike mendez . based on the screenplay by dan &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; and robert olsen , the film stars dolph lundgren as demon hunter &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; woodley , who travels to mississippi in the hopes of destroying an ancient , but homicidal demon . kristina &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , tony bentley , james &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , and miles &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , all star in supporting roles . after being postponed on two separate occasions , principal photography commenced in canton , mississippi over the 2015 christmas holiday season ; filming concluded after 17 days of shooting . do n't kill it had its worldwide premiere at the fantasy filmfest in hamburg , germany on august 27 , 2016 . this was followed by the north american premiere on september 26 , 2016 , at the fantastic fest film festival in austin , texas . do n't kill it received a limited theatrical release on march 3 , 2017 , and opened to mostly positive reviews . noel murray , of the the los angeles times , called the film one of lundgren 's " most entertaining movies in years . "